mktest 1.0
	simple tool for autogenerate projects of libraries
	and autogenerate Makefiles

USAGE:

	mktest
	mktest --help
	mktest --template xlib
			  sdl2_image
			  imlib2
			  curl
	mktest --editor emacs
			nvim
			vim
			vi

IN DOCUMENT:

	//mod editor-> emacs
		       nvim
		       vim
		       vi
	       debug-> true
	       compiler-> g++
	       		  clang++
